    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving 3.6L M96 flat-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque delivery across the rev range, optimized by VarioCam Plus valve timing. This example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a dry rear main seal, ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis retains its signature telepathic feedback through a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and McPherson strut front end. Braking performance is sharp, utilizing four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated rotors for consistent thermal management. An analog, driver-centric machine that bridges the gap between classic feel and modern performance.",
