      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the expected minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all onboard technology\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from rigorous adherence to scheduled maintenance. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring the next owner enjoys a turn-key experience. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. This car has been a non-smoker\u2019s vehicle, kept garaged when not in use, and comes with a complete set of service records and a clean title. It is an ideal choice for a discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality ride that has been treated with care.",
